Class ProductFormPolynomial

java.lang.Object
com.distrimind.bouncycastle.pqc.math.ntru.polynomial.ProductFormPolynomial
All Implemented Interfaces:
Polynomial
public class ProductFormPolynomial extends Object implements Polynomial
A polynomial of the form f1*f2+f3, where f1,f2,f3 are very sparsely populated ternary polynomials.
